# V8 package

- Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
- v8-cmake/V8 version: @V8_VERSION@
- LLVM toolchain: @LLVM_VERSION@
- Upstream archive: https://github.com/bnoordhuis/v8-cmake/archive/refs/tags/@V8_VERSION@.tar.gz

This package contains V8 public headers and the static libraries produced by
v8-cmake. It is intended as an input for PostgreSQL PL/V8 builds.

The current package is x86_64 Linux only. Other targets need a separate
host-tool build for torque and mksnapshot before target V8 libraries can be
cross-compiled reliably.
